<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She juggles her successful fashion career with being a mother to her three-year-old daughter Lea.</p>

<p>But Irina Shayk proved there's no rest for the wicked as she took part in Vogue Germany photoshoot at the Grand Hotel Villa D'Este in Lake Como earlier this month.</p>

<p>The supermodel, 34, ensured all eyes were on her as she slipped into a series of stylish ensembles while posing up a storm on a boat.</p>

<p> Busy bee: Irina Shayk proved there's no rest for the wicked as she took part in Vogue Germany photoshoot at the Grand Hotel Villa D'Este in Lake Como earlier this month</p>

<p>For one outfit, the Russian bombshell flashed her toned abs in a grey strapless bralet and a matching skirt, which she styled with a black bra. </p>

<p>The Victoria's Secret star continued to turn heads by switching into a shiny tasselled slip dress, which she wore with white slippers during brief breaks. </p>

<p>A chunky silver necklace served as the media personality's statement accessory, which complemented her dark black nail polish. </p>

<p>For her final look, the catwalk queen nailed vampy chic in a sheer bodysuit with a dramatic cape, paired with PVC thigh-high stiletto boots. </p>

